  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Contained within this small glass tube is a twisted wire filament crackling with electricity, sending static prickling through the hair of anyone holding it. The spell DC of any spell cast by activating this item is 17.</p><ul><li><strong>Armor</strong> You gain resistance 2 to electricity.</li><li><strong>Weapon</strong> After you cast an electricity spell by activating the coil, your Strikes with the weapon deal an additional 1d4 electricity damage until the end of your next turn.</li></ul><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.9mIS76oZkxXQ4g3T]{Effect: Jolt Coil - Armor}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.FZINfOjnuIeg0ZKo]{Effect: Jolt Coil - Weapon}</p><p>@Check[reflex|dc:17|basic|name:Jolt Coil Spell|traits:spell|showDC:all]</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.kBhaPuzLUSwS6vVf]{Electric Arc}.</p>"
